Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Huge Exposure + Parking on Pacific Hwy
Natural Light, Floor to Ceiling Glass

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located at one of the busiest intersections in Chatswood, opposite the corner of Pacific Highway & Albert Avenue, these brand new suites range in size from 230sqm to 1,500sqm. Offering natural light, prime exposure and an abundance of customer parking, these suites would be ideal for medical operators looking to work side by side with likeminded businesses.

+ Up to seven tenancies on offer over two different levels: 
- Upper ground floor – From 230sqm - 1,500sqm* (tenancies can be combined to create larger suites)
- Lower ground floor – 380sqm - 600sqm*
- Corner tenancy – LEASED! 
+ Parking for up to 41 cars
+ Air conditioning throughout 
+ Excellent signage opportunities (subject to approvals), passed by tens of thousands of cars daily
+ Occupying the whole block, the building sits in between Oliver and Freeman Road with over 100m* of glass shopfront facing Pacific Highway
+ Abundance of natural light with floor to ceiling glass windows throughout
+ Direct lift access from the main tenancies to the car park
+ Direct lift access from the main tenancies to the loading dock
+ Fully fitted male & female amenities on each level
+ Disabled access compliant throughout
+ Additional storage available (if required)
+ Located at the base of a mixed-use development with 72 apartments above
+ Walk to Chatswood Interchange, Westfield, trains and buses and the retail strip of Victoria Avenue
+ Adjacent to Chatswood BMW and surrounded by residential apartment blocks, commercial office towers and minutes to both Chatswood Primary School and High School

This beautifully presented, brand new development would suit would suit retail, showroom, medical, office, education or health & wellbeing (STCA).

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please call Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401.


*approx

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Currently leased to Mortgage Choice, this well-presented mezzanine office space sits metres from Chatswood Interchange and offers excellent branding opportunities on both the ground and first floor. 

+ 120sqm*  
+ Fit out in place including bathrooms, kitchen, boardroom and offices
+ Air conditioned 
+ Exclusive entrance off Victoria Avenue with large glass windows, ideal for branding/signage (STCA)
+ Located at the base of a commercial office tower, opposite Chatswood Interchange (trains & buses) and only minutes to all the retail and food & beverage Chatswood has to offer 
+ Premises can be handed over with fit out in place or brought back to a shell
+ Parking available if required 

To arrange an inspection, please call Tom Bennett 0430 924 629 or Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401.
